description:
My place is private room for one person in the heart of Chinatown resident area. The living room, the bathroom and kitchen are shared with other 2 bedrooms' guests.

It's close to Cermak-Chinatown Redline Station. Several bus stations are about 5mins walk.

15 mins to Loop and McCormick Place.

You can enjoy tons of Chinese food in Chinatown.

Street parking can be found on 22nd Pl and 23rd St, but do read the signage, as some streets have parking limits or are residential permit parking only.

On the first floor.
A private room with your own locker.
A shared living room, share bathroom and shared kitchen.

Center of Chinatown.
Close to Starbucks, Walgreens, Chinese supermarkets.

5 mins to Cermak-Chinatown Red Line Station;
5 mins to several bus station;
5 mins drive, 10 mins bus or 20 mins walk to McCormick Place;
10-15 mins to Downtown Chicago, Loop;
20 miles to O'Hare International Airport;
9 miles to Midway International Airport.

