description:
Cozy and comfortable studio with a full kitchen and clean bathroom. 

☺ Queen-sized bed, additional inflatable bed if needed;
☺ Washing and dryer machines available with fee charge;
☺ Safe neighborhood;
☺ Kitchenware provided, including pan, pot, and microwave, etc.

Guests will have full access to the studio.

☺ 1 min walk to Demster CTA station (purple line), ~30 min to Chicago downtown);
☺ 5-7 min walk to Evanston downtown;
☺ 3 min walk to two nearby groceries (Jewel-Osco and Trader Joe's);
☺ 10 min walk to the Northwestern University campus.

The studio is furnished. Below is a list of furnitures offered: 

- 1 mattress
- 1 desk
- 1 chair
- 1 rod Garment Rack and hangers
- kitchenware (e,g,  pan, pot, and microwave, etc.)
- 1 wardrobe
- 1 printer
- 1 kettle

